{"tid":1764023,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家想唔想同林鄭月峨宣戰？","createTime":"2019-11-30T19:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T03:45:48.000Z","uid":229494,"like":46,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"faa943eea9fa17d33d02b852c7ca17726841cef8","tid":1764023,"uid":229494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T19:37:44.000Z","msg":"你可能話：下？我哋一直咪打緊仗囉，而家先退步返去宣戰？ <br />\n<br />\n其實我哋似「掙扎」多過反抗，因為覺醒做勇武既人唔多，亦少左近身同popo隻揪既埸面，你見幾多身手唔錯既年輕人走去「做人鏈送物資」就知靠相對少量既勇武係完全唔可以蠃，亦對勇武手足唔公平。而家既行動完全配唔上「香港人報仇」呢句口號。<br />\n<br />\n要宣戰，就要有實在剛性既威脅，例如極強大既工會，真罷工可以connect外資，一齊令政府跪。<br />\n唔好同我講無可能，因為你條撚樣唔幫手先至無可能。我唔敢企最前線，但我可以餓一個月、訓一個月街<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=972e462e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\n如果有任何問題，先睇左谷內資料再講"},{"pid":"2c99167b00f2c9ea43539064bb73e54ee4bce83a","tid":1764023,"uid":229494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T19:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13e9cb5abd70cdfc1c240584c9a05aeef75755c","tid":1764023,"uid":229494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T19:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfb4140e7e967645d66a83594a30cff4cbc4f1e","tid":1764023,"uid":32906,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T19:40:47.000Z","msg":"已經存緊錢同罐頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af50e912493a131ef9f0e120f6ec9e2695a23134","tid":1764023,"uid":229494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T19:40:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"64711f9b45655eb9a39b7cd7e11e790f8cdbc041","tid":1764023,"uid":229494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bfb4140e7e967645d66a83594a30cff4cbc4f1e","tid":1764023,"uid":32906,"like":3,